@startuml 支付系统架构图（高管汇报版）

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E6F3FF
  BorderColor #2E86AB
  FontColor #0A2463
  FontSize 14
  ArrowColor #2E86AB
}

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F0F8FF
  BorderColor #2E86AB
  FontColor #0A2463
  FontSize 12
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF8E6
  BorderColor #FFB366
  FontColor #8B4513
  FontSize 11
}

title 支付系统架构图（高管汇报版）

' 外部实体
actor 用户 as user
actor 商户 as merchant
actor 第三方支付 as bank_payment

' 业务价值层
rectangle "业务价值" as business_value {
  [提升支付成功率] as success_rate
  [降低支付成本] as cost_reduction
  [增强支付安全] as security_enhancement
  [提升用户体验] as user_experience
  [支持业务增长] as business_growth
}

' 核心业务能力层
rectangle "核心业务能力" as core_capabilities {
  [全渠道支付] as omni_channel_payment
  [智能风控] as intelligent_risk
  [渠道自助切换] as channel_switching
  [实时清算] as realtime_settlement
  [商户管理] as merchant_management
}

' 技术平台层
rectangle "技术平台" as tech_platform {
  [支付核心平台] as payment_core
  [风控引擎] as risk_engine
  [渠道管理平台] as channel_management
  [清结算平台] as settlement_platform
  [商户服务平台] as merchant_service
}

' 基础设施层
rectangle "基础设施" as infrastructure {
  [云服务] as cloud_service
  [大数据平台] as bigdata_platform
  [安全服务] as security_service
  [监控告警] as monitoring_service
}

' 连接关系
user --> business_value : 享受服务
merchant --> business_value : 获得收益
bank_payment --> tech_platform : 提供支付渠道

business_value --> core_capabilities : 由业务能力支撑
core_capabilities --> tech_platform : 由技术平台实现
tech_platform --> infrastructure : 依赖基础设施

' 业务能力与技术平台的具体映射
omni_channel_payment --> payment_core : 由支付核心平台支撑
intelligent_risk --> risk_engine : 由风控引擎支撑
channel_switching --> channel_management : 由渠道管理平台支撑
realtime_settlement --> settlement_platform : 由清结算平台支撑
merchant_management --> merchant_service : 由商户服务平台支撑

' 技术平台与基础设施的具体映射
payment_core --> cloud_service : 部署于云服务
risk_engine --> bigdata_platform : 依赖大数据平台
channel_management --> cloud_service : 部署于云服务
settlement_platform --> bigdata_platform : 依赖大数据平台
merchant_service --> cloud_service : 部署于云服务

' 安全服务连接到所有技术平台
security_service --> payment_core : 提供安全保障
security_service --> risk_engine : 提供安全保障
security_service --> channel_management : 提供安全保障
security_service --> settlement_platform : 提供安全保障
security_service --> merchant_service : 提供安全保障

' 监控告警连接到所有技术平台
monitoring_service --> payment_core : 提供监控告警
monitoring_service --> risk_engine : 提供监控告警
monitoring_service --> channel_management : 提供监控告警
monitoring_service --> settlement_platform : 提供监控告警
monitoring_service --> merchant_service : 提供监控告警

note left of business_value
  <b>业务价值亮点:</b>
  • 支付成功率提升至99.9%
  • 支付成本降低30%
  • 欺诈损失率低于0.01%
  • 用户支付体验满意度提升40%
  • 支持每年50%的业务增长
end note

note right of core_capabilities
  <b>核心业务能力:</b>
  • 支持微信、支付宝、银联等全渠道支付
  • 基于AI的实时风控系统
  • 一键式支付渠道自助切换
  • T+0实时清算能力
  • 全生命周期商户管理
end note

note bottom of tech_platform
  <b>技术平台优势:</b>
  • 高可用架构，支持99.99%系统可用性
  • 弹性扩展，支持每秒10万+交易
  • 模块化设计，支持快速迭代
  • 安全合规，符合支付行业标准
  • 开放API，支持快速接入
end note

@enduml
